  1. T-16

Andy Tate - Guitar/Vocals
Charlie Passarell - Bass/Backups
Jeffrey Hollandsworth - Drums/Percussion

Mos Likely is a new Star Wars inspired garage rock band out of Sacramento, California. We are currently recording our first full length album. "I'm Somebody Special" is an EP release of 3 acoustic demos I (Andy Tate) recorded and sent to the rest of the band to learn. I hope you guys enjoy! Give us some feed back! Check the links below for new updates and music!

For fans of Jeffrey Lewis, Weezer, Pavement, Built To Spill, Modest Mouse, The Mountain Goats, The Thermals, Black Eyes etc...
